EngineeringDataManager.DataManager.get_node_data — Method
get_node_data(w_node::ParameterValueNode)

Returns nodes data field content for a single node of ParameterValueNode type

Returns named tuple: (name = param_name, - the name of the parameter id = id, - paramater/property id data = data, - data (parsed to vector) qualifier = qual - qualifier )

source
EngineeringDataManager.DataManager.get_prop_id_by_prop_name — Method
get_prop_id_by_prop_name(property_name)

As far as NAMES dictionary stores both properties and parameters associated to the property name, this function is used to get property id pr* from the property name (otherwise it returns error)

source
